00:00:00,160 --> 00:00:04,750
Human fascination with animals goes back as far as humans do

2
00:00:05,120 --> 00:00:07,830
Of the oldest cave paintings discovered

3
00:00:07,920 --> 00:00:11,210
some are up to 40000 years old

4
00:00:11,220 --> 00:00:14,770
and there are more images of animals than humans

5
00:00:15,390 --> 00:00:16,480
At some point

6
00:00:16,520 --> 00:00:20,020
