13
00:00:40,530 --> 00:00:42,600
They probably had short lives

14
00:00:42,710 --> 00:00:45,940
and the remains show evidence of severe injuries

15
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:55,790
The first public exhibit of animals may have been created by Egypt Queen hat chesu around 1480 BC

16
00:00:55,930 --> 00:01:01,860
Researchers think the zoo was started with animals brought home from a far off land known as Punt

17
00:01:02,220 --> 00:01:04,800
It's unclear why the queen built the zoo

18
00:01:04,970 --> 00:01:08,280
